{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, we conclude support for H1.",
    "The second hypothesis (H2) stated that a high (vs. low) TMT AI literacy increases a firm's HR-related AI implementation ability.",
    "We tested H2 with model 2 in Table 2.",
    "In model 2, we also control for a potential influence of AI orientation on HR-related AI implementation ability.",
    "TMT AI literacy positively affects HR-related AI implementation ability (β = 0.795, p <.001)."
  ]
}